<note place="bottomcentral"><ab facs="#facs_301_r1l29">Jn Berthold <expan>kandelgieſſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> hawſe cʒü <expan>Heylprun<ex>n</ex>e</expan> / . </ab></note>
